# Researcher — improve pass 2 (bowling-shirt-designer)

Delta over researcher.out. Base sections (§1 library versions, §2 next.config, §3 scaffold, §6–8 Tailwind/fonts/store-skeleton, §10–16 backend/PHP/workSamples/API/CSS/AuditSection/manifest) are unchanged — demo-builder reads them from researcher.out. Only the sections that change are written here.

---

## §1 ADDITION — new npm dependency

```bash
npm install @imgly/background-removal
```

- Package: `@imgly/background-removal` (latest stable ~1.4.5)
- Self-fetches ONNX model from jsDelivr CDN at first `removeBackground()` call (~12–60 MB, cached after first load). No local model file needed.
- WASM runs transparently on WebGPU if `navigator.gpu` is available; falls back to CPU WASM automatically.
- Tree-shakeable; only imported inside `smartAlign.ts` behind a dynamic `import()`.

