- produced: improve-pass-2 researcher — new library (@imgly/background-removal), updated store.ts (front/back images + per-image transform state), full compositor.ts (2048² CanvasTexture with FRONT px512–1536 / BACK px0–512+1536–2048 UV islands, rAF-throttled recompose), full smartAlign.ts (deterministic alpha/variance bbox + lazy imgly WASM refine + boxToTransform), ShirtCanvas.tsx key changes (CylinderGeometry + vertex-displaced bowlifi profile, meshPhysicalMaterial sheen, knit normal map, Environment+ContactShadows+directionalLight), OptionsPanel additions (mode toggle, ImageUploadSlot with sliders + smart-align button), Poly Haven CORS check command, updated workSamples description.
- decisions: CylinderGeometry radialSegments=48 heightSegments=8 + post-construction vertex displacement for bowlifi silhouette (no GLB); single 2048² CanvasTexture compositor, FRONT=px512–1536, BACK-L=px0–512, BACK-R=px1536–2048; wrap-one fills all 2048px; @imgly lazy import behind try/catch (deterministic bbox is always the instant result); Poly Haven knit_fabric_02 nor_gl_1k.jpg (vendor if CORS 4xx); meshPhysicalMaterial sheen=0.9/sheenRoughness=0.45/roughness=0.85 as locked in planner3.
- next needs: demo-builder (1) npm install @imgly/background-removal; (2) CORS-check Poly Haven URL and vendor jpg if needed; (3) write compositor.ts + smartAlign.ts exactly as above; (4) apply surgical edits to store.ts, ShirtCanvas.tsx, OptionsPanel.tsx; (5) verify compositor UV islands match the actual CylinderGeometry seam position (log a vertex UV at angle=0 and confirm it's at U=0); (6) rebuild + verify smart-align visibly repositions the pattern.
- risks: CylinderGeometry seam placement (U=0) may not land exactly at back-center — verify with a UV-debug gradient texture before finalizing the px512/1536 split; @imgly 12–60 MB first-load is slow on mobile (spinner shown, deterministic result is immediate); sheenColor must be updated with `new THREE.Color(state.bodyColor)` when bodyColor changes (not just on mount).
